###user register
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Shree",
    "lastName": "user",
    "email": "shreeja123@gmail.com",
    "password": "user@1234",
    "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/avatars.png"
}

###author register
